                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Below 50 MeV, where the monitor reaction did not work,",
                "the standard beam current monitor of the cyclotron was",
                "used to relate the measurements."
              ]
            }
          ],
